name: BarnSoundsforSleep
0:

”Alexa ask barn sounds to play for 30 minutes”

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: barn sounds
des: Howdy! Let the calming sound of a barnyard get you ready for bed. Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Barn Sounds,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
